  "page": "Feature quote/103",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Power resides where men believe it resides. No more and no less.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a><br />“So power is a mummer's trick?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a><br />“A shadow on the wall, yet shadows can kill. And ofttimes a very small man can cast a very large shadow.” — <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>&lt;references&gt;\n</p>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Tyrion II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404205205\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 67/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8402/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 293/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 17/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 175/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.663      1 -total\n100.00%    4.663      1 Template:Ref\n 59.99%    2.797      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:10463-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404205